2	 * TypeScript types for .yoke.yml configuration.
3	 *
4	 * Derived from docs/design/schemas/yoke-config.schema.json (JSON Schema draft-2020-12).
5	 * Version "1" is the only supported version.
6	 *
7	 * Two forms:
8	 *   RawConfig      — direct YAML parse output; path fields may be relative strings.
9	 *   ResolvedConfig — RawConfig with all path fields guaranteed to be absolute,
10	 *                    plus a `configDir` field. All downstream modules consume
11	 *                    ResolvedConfig only.
12	 *
13	 * Resolved at load time (relative → absolute, base = .yoke.yml directory):
14	 *   phases[*].prompt_template
15	 *   phases[*].cwd                          (if present)
16	 *   phases[*].output_artifacts[*].schema   (if present)
17	 *   worktrees.teardown.script              (if present)
18	 *
19	 * NOT resolved (runtime-relative to the worktree, unknown at load time):
20	 *   pipeline.stages[*].items_from
21	 *   phases[*].output_artifacts[*].path
22	 */
